sentences: Per Erik Hallin (born 7 January 1950) is a Swedish keyboard player, singer and
Hallin played and sang with Elvis Presley in 1974.
Hallin took part in the Swedish Melodifestivalen in 1984 and 1985.
In 2006, he won the Artur Erikson-stipend.
